{"_id":"Creamyturkeycourgetteandpotatobake","preptime":"20","servings":"4","keywords":["cook method.hob, oven, grill@oven","diet@corn-free","diet@yeast-free","main ingredient@poultry","meal type@main","diet@egg-free","special collections@weekday meal","diet@wheat-free","diet@peanut-free","special collections@very easy","diet@citrus-free","diet@shellfish-free","main ingredient@vegetables","diet@demi-veg","main ingredient@rice, potatoes, grains, couscous","special collections@all-in-one recipe","diet@gluten-free"],"subtitle":"A good all-in-one recipe.","totaltime":"80","cooktime":"60","ingredients":[{"ingredient":"minced turkey","measure":"450 g"},{"ingredient":"garlic","measure":"1 clove"},{"ingredient":"large onion","measure":"1"},{"ingredient":"mature cheddar cheese","measure":"100 g"},{"ingredient":"fresh chives","measure":"3 tsp"},{"ingredient":"potatoes","measure":"450 g"},{"ingredient":"courgettes","measure":"2"},{"ingredient":"single cream","measure":"300 ml"},{"ingredient":"seasoning","measure":""},{"ingredient":"paprika","measure":"[sup]1[/sup]/[sub]2[/sub] tsp"}],"method":[{"step":"1","text":"Preheat oven to 180&deg;C."},{"step":"2","text":"In a bowl, mix together the turkey, garlic and onion. Spoon into a lightly greased ovenproof dish. Scatter over the cheese and chives."},{"step":"3","text":"Layer the potato and courgette slices on top of the turkey. "},{"step":"4","text":"In a jug, mix together the cream and seasoning. Pour into the dish allowing time for it to settle."},{"step":"5","text":"Sprinkle over a little paprika. Place on a baking tray in the oven for 60-90 min until tender and well browned."}],"title":"Creamy turkey, courgette and potato bake"}